│  5 │ 00:35:48 │ move │ ~/Downloads/song.mp3                         │ ~/Organized/music/song.mp3                               │ completed │
│  6 │ 00:35:48 │ move │ ~/Downloads/unknown.xyz                      │ ~/Organized/other/unknown.xyz                            │ completed │
